videos.description: Kansas State's Dean Wade leads Xavier Sneed in transition for an emphatic one-handed dunk.
videos.headline: Sneed soars for transition slam

videos.description: Barry Brown drives down the lane and converts the and-1 layup for Kansas State.
videos.headline: Brown sinks tough layup for and-1 opportunity

videos.description: Kansas State's Kamau Stokes dishes the ball to Dean Wade inside for a layup.
videos.headline: Wade spins to convert post lay-in

videos.description: Texas Tech's Niem Stevenson tries taking it inside for a lay-in but is rejected by Kansas State's Dean Wade.
videos.headline: Wade denies Stevenson in the paint

videos.description: Texas Tech's Jarrett Culver swings the ball over to Tommy Hamilton in the corner for a 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Hamilton drains corner 3-pointer

videos.description: Texas Tech's Keenan Evans kicks the ball out to Jarrett Culver for a 3-pointer late in the first half.
videos.headline: Culver nails 3-pointer to even game

videos.description: Texas Tech's Keenan Evans drives down the lane and converts a Eurostep lay-in, earning a trip to the line for a 3-point play.
videos.headline: Evans finishes Eurostep layup for and-1 chance

videos.description: Niem Stevenson swings the ball over to Tommy Hamilton for a 3-pointer to extend Texas Tech's lead.
videos.headline: Hamilton converts third straight 3-pointer

videos.description: Texas Tech's Niem Stevenson finds Zhaire Smith in the paint for a two-handed dunk.
videos.headline: Stevenson finds Smith for two-handed slam
